Fresh Pi session: CODE REVIEW (agentic, round {{run.round}}).

Inputs:
- Execution status: {{run.dir}}/execution/status-{{run.round}}.json
- Execution summary: {{run.dir}}/execution/summary-{{run.round}}.md
- Manual-testing report: {{run.dir}}/manual-testing/report-{{run.round}}.md
- Issues from prior rounds (if any): {{run.issues-file}}
- Worktree (repository root): {{run.worktree-dir}}

Goal:
Perform a pass/fail code review of the changes in the worktree, consuming the execution + manual-testing evidence. Confirm each change item from changes-needed/changes.json is actually addressed and that tests pass.

Rules:
- Inspect the repository diff and run checks as needed.
- Do not edit source code; review only (read-only tools).
- Do not push or create pull requests.
- Map every failure to a concrete issue; do not fail without a reason.

Write:
- Report: {{run.dir}}/review/report-{{run.round}}.md
- Status: {{run.dir}}/review/status-{{run.round}}.json
- If failing: {{run.dir}}/review/issues-{{run.round}}.json

Status JSON examples:
{"status":"pass","summary":"all change items verified","issues_file":null}
{"status":"fail","summary":"change item 3 not addressed","issues_file":"review/issues-{{run.round}}.json"}